  <dashboards>
    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 1'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Understanding the Differences Between Casual Riders and Members</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='1460' maxwidth='2350' sizing-mode='range' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98120' id='14' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99034' x='483' y='940'>
            <zone h='5875' id='15' type-v2='title' w='99034' x='483' y='940'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='92245' id='8' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99034' x='483' y='6815'>
              <zone h='92245' id='6' type-v2='layout-basic' w='89378' x='483' y='6815'>
                <zone h='46121' id='3' name='Average Ride Length by Rider Type' w='26736' x='35061' y='6815'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='46124' id='5' name='Sheet 2' w='34578' x='483' y='52936'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='46121' id='10' name='Sheet 3' w='34578' x='483' y='6815'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='46124' id='11' name='Sheet 4' w='26736' x='35061' y='52936'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='46123' id='16' type-v2='text' w='28064' x='61797' y='6815'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Key Insights</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Casual riders take rides 58% longer than members.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Casual riders show strong weekend usage patterns.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Members exhibit commuter behaviour, with pronounced ride peaks at 8 AM and 5 PM.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Both rider groups strongly prefer electric bikes.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Casual riders appear to use Cyclistic primarily for leisure, while members use it as part of their regular transportation routine.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='46122' id='21' type-v2='text' w='28064' x='61797' y='52938'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Business Recommendations</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>• Launch weekend-to-membership campaigns targeting frequent casual riders.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>• Introduce commuter challenges to encourage weekday riding.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>• Position membership as a transportation solution rather than a leisure product.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>• Leverage the popularity of electric bikes through member-exclusive benefits.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
